item.title: Mike Salter
item.dc:creator: ins_roofing$
item.content:encoded: These guys aren’t your typical roofing company. They are fair, thorough, and shoot you straight. I’ll put it to you this way, if the employees are happy and love what they do, it speaks volumes about the company.

item.title: Bret Moody
item.dc:creator: ins_roofing$
item.content:encoded: I’m glad that you are the ones who fixed my roof. You are a hard working crew and nice to have around. These guys aren’t your typical roofing company. I will definitely recommend your company to my friends.
